name: BIRDLILY BLUE RED PATTERN
description:
A digital print of an original design by Karen Schaeper.  Prints are signed on the reverse by the designer.

Karen Schaeper is a Sydney based colour and graphic designer. The designs focus on simplicity of shape with minimal palettes to provide a lively, vibrant colour impact to your space.

Designs are commercially printed on 280 gsm - Linen Embossed Alpine Ivory Board which is acid free, archival quality.

The prints are A4 (210mm x 297mm) in size and sold UNFRAMED. 

Designs fit an Ikea - Ribba frame size (300mm x 400mm) with a mount area of (200mm x 290mm) as seen in image.

Prints are sealed in a cello bag with boxboard and mailed in a sturdy Jiffy Rigi Mailer.

Designs are the property of © Karen Schaeper and cannot be reproduced without the designer's permission.  Watermarks will not be visible on purchased prints.

name: BOTTLE GIFT TAGS - BIRD LILY
description:
The perfect accessory for the bottle gift.  No wrapping required which is great for our planet.  Tags are easy to attach, look great with either wine or champagne bottles and come with 6 different printed messages which means you'll have a tag on hand for every occasion.   

The tags are 60mm x 125mm in dimension, printed on one side only with space on the front for your name or you can add your own personal message to the back.  

Original designs are printed to 220 gsm watercolour paper, include reinforced holes with a white nylon pre-tied cord.

All designs are the property of © Karen Schaeper and cannot be reproduced without the designer's permission.  Watermarks will not be visible on purchased prints.
